                            <strong style="color:#62c92b">@ViewBag.percentpay</strong> %)：
                            <strong class="ftx-01" id="RealPrice">@(((decimal)ViewBag.RealPrice).ToString("F2"))</strong>@ViewBag.paydanwei  &nbsp;
